  • java.lang.Object

    public class QSet
extends Object
implements AppConstants, QuestionConstants, TopicQSetConstants
    A question set for editing. Corresponds to the authoring session.

      • addQuestion

        public Question addQuestion(Question question)
                     throws DBException,
                            ParameterException
        Adds a question. Messages can be obtained by calling getDbMessage(). If the question was duplicated from another question, a new qId is assigned when it is about to be written to the database. Any translations associated with unmodified portions of the duplicated question are preserved and assigned new phraseId values.
        Parameters:
        question - the question to be saved
        Returns:
        the added question, or null if it could not be saved
        Throws:
        DBException - if there's a problem writing to the database
        ParameterException - never

      • loadStoredResponses

        public void loadStoredResponses()
                         throws InvalidOpException,
                                DBException,
                                ParameterException
        Loads all the response history of the current question. Must be called before calling getStoredResponses(). Cannot apply to R-group questions because each response will have different R groups associated with them, and they are not stored with the logged responses.
        Throws:
        DBException - if there's a problem reading the database
        InvalidOpException - if the question is not valid
        ParameterException - if an invalid index to an evaluator, question datum, or evaluator is given

        public String parseXML(NodeList nodeList,
